summary: An Ordinance appropriating the sum of $8.64, or so much thereof as may be necessary from the General Fund of the City of Seattle, for the purpose of paying the 1909 general taxes on the E. 40 feet of E. 1/2 of the N. 1/2 of the N. 1/2 of the NE 1/4 of NW 1/4 of section 35, township 24, range 3, and for the purpose of paying the 1910 general taxes on the West 5 feet of tract 5, Wilson & Bryans Tracts.
